FT  19 SEP 92 / World News In Brief: Mine blast kills nine
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Police have launched an investigation after nine miners were killed in an
underground explosion at the Royal Oak gold mine in northern Canada.
Replacement workers were working at the mine, which has been the target of a
strike since May.
