year, while further sales gains were expected when the Bentall Centre opened
in November.
Agreement had been reached to sell the Bentalls charge card business to GE
Capital. The move would reduce borrowings by more than Pounds 6m.
Turnover edged ahead by Pounds 1m to Pounds 31.5m. Losses per share were
