Foreign Staff writes.
It showed a marginal rise from 53 per cent recorded in the previous two days
but was down from its peak of a 56 per cent Yes on September 7 and 8. The
low point was a 50 per cent dead heat on August 25.
Bettors specify the outcome they expect when placing their stake. Winners
are repaid this amount for each percentage point between the result and the
level they were quoted.
